Stripe configuration is now loaded from the WordPress environment.

Set these in wp-config.php or your server environment:

KIBSTERLP_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE=your_publishable_key
KIBSTERLP_STRIPE_SECRET=your_secret_key

Example in wp-config.php:

define('KIBSTERLP_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE', getenv('KIBSTERLP_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE'));
define('KIBSTERLP_STRIPE_SECRET', getenv('KIBSTERLP_STRIPE_SECRET'));
